{"tid":47382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退休交警偷竊囚20個月 官：做唔成差人唔一定要做壞人","createTime":"2016-12-20T10:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T12:00:57.000Z","uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4215cac35afef549b204dd2d7b8deab75990dc24","tid":47382,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161220/56069857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161220%2F56069857&d=kYqbks8eUmnrBUD5tZVkznvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1120db14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161220%2F56069857&h=00bc3db6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161220/56069857</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161220/large/1482204776_a703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161220%2Flarge%2F1482204776_a703.jpg&h=4fcdd748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳榮佳(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n效力警隊32年的交通警因隱瞞干犯危駕案而被勒令退休，從此過著顛簸生活。他改行揸的士卻因經濟拮据而屢犯偷竊，他今年夥同黨爆竊食肆的夾萬，但被天眼拍下而被追捕。被告早前認罪，法官酌情准他保釋處理苦等多年才獲分配的公屋。案件今早在區院判刑，被告親口答謝法官給予時間，法官亦勉勵他出獄後要勤力搵工，謂「就算做唔成差人都唔一定要做壞人」。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳榮佳（59歲）被判入獄20個月。他的律師今早表示感謝法庭以人道立場批准押後，被告已取得公屋單位的鎖匙，並已安排親友暫時看管單位。被告亦說「多謝法官大人」。<br />\n<br />\n法官在判刑後主動向被告說，律師已盡力替他求情，但到了最後還是要靠被告自己。法官指，本案唯一興幸的是見到被告等了多年終於找到安身之所，他寄語被告出獄後安定好自己，重過簡單生活。"},{"pid":"f6aef66a713b718bd8836af34eca445fa7337b05","tid":47382,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"退休警得一分"},{"pid":"72d23a3ee2adb1a8b56c37eae80d8943cd22d66e","tid":47382,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"差人同壞人有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af79e4a03d8f8d6c119bcafbbf960e1fe6af7610","tid":47382,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0553e61796fdc17abe5291b59c087312ec0a1589","tid":47382,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差人同壞人有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee581978e335517a2749a1eefb3f4b91663f47b2","tid":47382,"uid":67298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"做32年幾皮野一個月都苦等公屋<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"4489ecf41a87b5b9ab6cf1ace7844ecf2ba122bb","tid":47382,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4142c32ac6223463675e363ea17b0ce005959987","tid":47382,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"差人咪就係壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}